WEBVTT



00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:05.984
Jerusalem is always inspiring to visit during the Jewish holidays.

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:08.768
And the biblical feast of tabernacles is

00:00:08.928 --> 00:00:12.064
Join us in the city of the great king for

00:00:11.744 --> 00:00:14.816
Five nights of joyful celebration.

00:00:14.848 --> 00:00:18.976
Exports Ministry has planned a special tour package.

00:00:18.752 --> 00:00:23.360
including participation with thousands of Israelis and guests.

00:00:23.168 --> 00:00:27.072
from all over the world in the annual Jerusalem March.

00:00:27.296 --> 00:00:29.728
So bring your flags banners

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:31.200
And walking shoes.

00:00:31.328 --> 00:00:35.040
We'll also explore many of the ancient wonders and

00:00:34.816 --> 00:00:37.632
Spiritual highlights around the city.

00:00:37.568 --> 00:00:40.800
And we'll have times of feasting and celebration.

00:00:41.344 --> 00:00:48.480
So plan now to come up to Jerusalem and join our tour and spiritual adventure.

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:51.008
For more details, visit our website at www.fema.org.

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:53.536
Jerusalem channel dot tv
